<p><b>Human Rights Council 
Eighteenth session 
</b>Agenda item 3 
<b>Promotion and protection of all human rights, civil, 
political, economic, social and cultural rights, 
including the right to development 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Albania</b>*<b>, Armenia</b>*<b>, Australia</b>*<b>, Austria, Benin, Bosnia and Herzegovina</b>*<b>, Bulgaria</b>*<b>, 
Canada</b>*<b>, Chile, Colombia</b>*<b>, Costa Rica, C&#244;te d&#8217;Ivoire</b>*<b>, Croatia</b>*<b>, Cuba, Czech 
